Team response: Hi @mohsinraza-fdev, I think this might be an issue with your debouncing logic. You could at certain points have the text show what you have typed but that would not be the request that is made. You can see what I mean by running your app in the web browser and checking the network requests. 

How did you come up with the logic for the debouncing? I think using a fixed delay might yield a more consistent result.

